CARLOS Quieroz could be announced as the new Bafana Bafana coach tomorrow, having been recommended by the Safa technical committee.The committee was tasked with finding a replacement for Shakes Mashaba, who was sacked in December and are understood to have put forward the name of Queiroz for the vacant position. Queiroz has emerged as firm favourite to land the position, ahead of Morocco coach Herve Renard.KGOMOTSO SETHUSHA